body_html:
Thanks for the note @jendap.

I'm wrapping the current C++ API with an Objective C++ interface in order to build a Swift-based iOS app. Complicated, I know! To do this, I'd created a set of Xcode projects to build both Protobuf and TensorFlow libs and am managing the build from there.
